title: Maninang Christoni maothi bias
lyrics:
Maninang Christoni maothi bias
Maninang subungkhow gumden giri -2
Benw Krushni biban, Benw Jiuni thangki -2
(a)
Majwng somai hwnw jebw gwiya
Majwng gwjwn hwnw jwng haoria
“Jwng bibaiari” -2
(b)
Gwsw mwdwm jiujwng borayw jwng
Onnanwi najaodw O guru -2
“Bwr hwdw jwngnw” -2
